sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 🖥️ Streamlit UI
    participant F as ⚡ FastAPI
    participant QE as 🧠 Query Engine
    participant CE as 🎯 Cross-Encoder
    participant LLM as 🤖 NVIDIA NIM

    U->>F: POST /query/stream
    F->>QE: retrieve_context(query)
    QE->>QE: Embed query (384d)
    QE->>QE: ChromaDB Top-16
    QE->>QE: BM25 + Vector Fusion
    QE->>CE: Cross-Encoder Re-rank
    CE->>QE: Top-3 Chunks
    QE->>QE: Graph 1-hop Traversal
    QE->>F: Context (chunks + graph)

    F->>LLM: stream_generate(prompt)
    
    loop Token Stream (SSE)
        LLM-->>F: token chunk
        F-->>U: data: {"type":"token","content":"..."}
        U->>U: Display token (instant)
    end

    LLM-->>F: stream complete
    F-->>U: data: {"type":"metadata","content":{sources,confidence,...}}
    F-->>U: data: {"type":"done","content":""}

    Note over F: try/finally ensures metadata+done always fire
    Note over U: First token appears in <100ms
